Pupitar (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0246: Larvitar
Pokémon
#0248: Tyranitar →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Pupitar (TCG Pocket).

Pupitar has been featured on 25 different cards since it debuted in the Neo Discovery expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Pupitar cards are normally Fighting-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Pupitar

Pupitar
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
